---

<BaseLayout
  title="Risorse — Marco Munich"
  description="Il percorso completo per sviluppare un Personal Branding Olistico autentico. Corsi gratuiti, libri, podcast e tutto quello che serve per promuoverti come voce diversa."
  currentPath="/risorse/"
>

<!-- ══ HERO ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="rs-hero">
  <div class="rs-hero__inner">

    <div class="rs-hero__profile">
      <img class="rs-hero__avatar" src="/og/marco-munich.png" alt="Marco Munich" width="88" height="88" />
      <div>
        <p class="rs-hero__name">Marco Munich</p>
        <p class="rs-hero__role">Personal Branding Olistico</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="rs-hero__claim">
      Sviluppa un punto di vista per promuoverti online come voce diversa dalle altre.
    </h1>

    <div class="rs-hero__audio-wrap">
      <p class="rs-hero__audio-label">Ascolta il messaggio di benvenuto</p>
      <audio controls class="rs-hero__audio" controlslist="nodownload" playsinline>
        <source src="/audio/nuovo-benvenuto-sito.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
      </audio>
    </div>

    <div class="rs-hero__social">
      {socials.map(s => (
        <a href={s.href} target="_blank" rel="nofollow" aria-label={s.label} class="rs-social-link">
          <Fragment set:html={s.icon} />
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <a href="https://wa.link/eemovr" target="_blank" class="rs-btn rs-btn--gold">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 448 512" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M380.9 97.1C339 55.1 283.2 32 223.9 32c-122.4 0-222 99.6-222 222 0 39.1 10.2 77.3 29.6 111L0 480l117.7-30.9c32.4 17.7 68.9 27 106.1 27h.1c122.3 0 224.1-99.6 224.1-222 0-59.3-25.2-115-67.1-157zm-157 341.6c-33.2 0-65.7-8.9-94-25.7l-6.7-4-69.8 18.3L72 359.2l-4.4-7c-18.5-29.4-28.2-63.3-28.2-98.2 0-101.7 82.8-184.5 184.6-184.5 49.3 0 95.6 19.2 130.4 54.1 34.8 34.9 56.2 81.2 56.1 130.5 0 101.8-84.9 184.6-186.6 184.6zm101.2-138.2c-5.5-2.8-32.8-16.2-37.9-18-5.1-1.9-8.8-2.8-12.5 2.8-3.7 5.6-14.3 18-17.6 21.8-3.2 3.7-6.5 4.2-12 1.4-32.6-16.3-54-29.1-75.5-66-5.7-9.8 5.7-9.1 16.3-30.3 1.8-3.7.9-6.9-.5-9.7-1.4-2.8-12.5-30.1-17.1-41.2-4.5-10.8-9.1-9.3-12.5-9.5-3.2-.2-6.9-.2-10.6-.2-3.7 0-9.7 1.4-14.8 6.9-5.1 5.6-19.4 19-19.4 46.3 0 27.3 19.9 53.7 22.6 57.4 2.8 3.7 39.1 59.7 94.8 83.8 35.2 15.2 49 16.5 66.6 13.9 10.7-1.6 32.8-13.4 37.4-26.4 4.6-13 4.6-24.1 3.2-26.4-1.3-2.5-5-3.9-10.5-6.6z"/>
      </svg>
      Chiacchierata Introduttiva
    </a>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ PERCORSO ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="rs-percorso">
  <div class="rs-percorso__inner">

    <div class="rs-section-head">
      <span class="rs-label">Il percorso</span>
      <h2 class="rs-section-title">Da dove <em>iniziare</em></h2>
      <p class="rs-section-sub">Segui questi passi nell'ordine che ti propongo. Ogni risorsa si appoggia sulla precedente.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rs-steps">
      {steps.map((step) => (
        <div class="rs-step" style={`background:${step.bg};border-top:3px solid ${step.border};`}>
          <span class="rs-step__n" style={`color:${step.color};`}>{step.n}</span>
          <div class="rs-step__content">
            <span class="rs-step__tag" style={`color:${step.color};`}>{step.tag}</span>
            <h3 class="rs-step__title">{step.titolo}</h3>
            <p class="rs-step__desc">{step.desc}</p>
            <div class="rs-step__actions">
              <a href={step.href} class="rs-btn" style={`background:${step.color};color:#fff;`}>{step.cta} →</a>
              {step.secondary && (
                <a href={step.secondary.href} class="rs-btn rs-btn--ghost">{step.secondary.cta}</a>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ VIDEO ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="rs-video">
  <div class="rs-video__inner">
    <div class="rs-video__wrap">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DW-Mj8QxPg8?rel=0&modestbranding=1"
        title="Marco Munich — Personal Branding Olistico"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ DELEGATE ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="rs-delegate">
  <div class="rs-delegate__inner">
    <span class="rs-label rs-label--light">Collaborazione</span>
    <h2 class="rs-delegate__title">Vuoi delegarmi <em>del lavoro?</em></h2>
    <p class="rs-delegate__sub">
      Se senti di avere già un messaggio autentico e cerchi qualcuno che ti
      metta in piedi un sistema di acquisizione clienti, considera una di queste opzioni.
    </p>

    <div class="rs-delegate__grid">
      <div class="rs-delegate__item rs-delegate__item--highlight">
        <span class="rs-delegate__badge">In evidenza</span>
        <h3 class="rs-delegate__item-title">Sviluppo Siti Web ad Alte Prestazioni</h3>
        <p class="rs-delegate__item-desc">Siti veloci, ottimizzati per i motori di ricerca e costruiti per convertire. Niente template generici: ogni progetto viene pensato attorno al tuo messaggio.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rs-delegate__item">
        <h3 class="rs-delegate__item-title">Sistema di Prenotazione Appuntamenti</h3>
        <p class="rs-delegate__item-desc">Installazione e configurazione del sistema automatico di prenotazione, così i tuoi clienti possono fissare una call senza passare per i messaggi.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rs-delegate__item">
        <h3 class="rs-delegate__item-title">Creazione Corso Online</h3>
        <p class="rs-delegate__item-desc">Trasformo le tue conoscenze in un corso strutturato e vendibile, dalla piattaforma alla pagina di vendita.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://wa.link/eemovr" target="_blank" class="rs-btn rs-btn--gold">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 448 512" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M380.9 97.1C339 55.1 283.2 32 223.9 32c-122.4 0-222 99.6-222 222 0 39.1 10.2 77.3 29.6 111L0 480l117.7-30.9c32.4 17.7 68.9 27 106.1 27h.1c122.3 0 224.1-99.6 224.1-222 0-59.3-25.2-115-67.1-157zm-157 341.6c-33.2 0-65.7-8.9-94-25.7l-6.7-4-69.8 18.3L72 359.2l-4.4-7c-18.5-29.4-28.2-63.3-28.2-98.2 0-101.7 82.8-184.5 184.6-184.5 49.3 0 95.6 19.2 130.4 54.1 34.8 34.9 56.2 81.2 56.1 130.5 0 101.8-84.9 184.6-186.6 184.6zm101.2-138.2c-5.5-2.8-32.8-16.2-37.9-18-5.1-1.9-8.8-2.8-12.5 2.8-3.7 5.6-14.3 18-17.6 21.8-3.2 3.7-6.5 4.2-12 1.4-32.6-16.3-54-29.1-75.5-66-5.7-9.8 5.7-9.1 16.3-30.3 1.8-3.7.9-6.9-.5-9.7-1.4-2.8-12.5-30.1-17.1-41.2-4.5-10.8-9.1-9.3-12.5-9.5-3.2-.2-6.9-.2-10.6-.2-3.7 0-9.7 1.4-14.8 6.9-5.1 5.6-19.4 19-19.4 46.3 0 27.3 19.9 53.7 22.6 57.4 2.8 3.7 39.1 59.7 94.8 83.8 35.2 15.2 49 16.5 66.6 13.9 10.7-1.6 32.8-13.4 37.4-26.4 4.6-13 4.6-24.1 3.2-26.4-1.3-2.5-5-3.9-10.5-6.6z"/>
      </svg>
      Contattami su WhatsApp
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ QUICK LINKS ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="rs-quicklinks">
  <div class="rs-quicklinks__inner">
    <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/2WwJsiCJYSZnawH2TQ6N2n" target="_blank" class="rs-quicklink">
      <span class="rs-quicklink__label">Podcast</span>
      <span class="rs-quicklink__name">Ascoltami su Spotify →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/" class="rs-quicklink">
      <span class="rs-quicklink__label">Contenuti</span>
      <span class="rs-quicklink__name">Leggi il Blog →</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/chi-sono/" class="rs-quicklink">
      <span class="rs-quicklink__label">La storia</span>
      <span class="rs-quicklink__name">Chi sono →</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

.rs-label {
  font: 700 0.62rem/1 var(--sans);
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.rs-label--light { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }

/* ── Buttons ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.rs-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font: 700 0.78rem/1 var(--sans);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.85rem 1.6rem;
  border-radius: 1px;
  transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s, transform 0.12s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.rs-btn--gold  { background: #25D366; color: #fff; }
.rs-btn--gold:hover { background: #1da851; transform: translateY(-1px); opacity: 1; }
.rs-btn--dark  { background: #25D366; color: #fff; }
.rs-btn--dark:hover { background: #1da851; transform: translateY(-1px); opacity: 1; }
.rs-btn--ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--muted); padding-left: 0; }
.rs-btn--ghost:hover { color: var(--black); opacity: 1; }

/* ══ HERO ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.rs-hero {
  background: var(--black);
  padding: 6rem var(--pad) 5rem;
}
.rs-hero__inner {
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  gap: 2rem;
}
.rs-hero__profile {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.25rem;
}
.rs-hero__avatar {
  width: 80px; height: 80px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.rs-hero__name {
  font: 700 0.72rem/1 var(--sans);
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  text-align: left;
}
.rs-hero__role {
  font: 300 0.85rem/1.3 var(--sans);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38);
  text-align: left;
}
.rs-hero__claim {
  font: 300 clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem)/1.5 var(--serif);
  font-style: italic;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  max-width: 480px;
}
.rs-hero__audio-wrap { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; }
.rs-hero__audio-label {
  display: block;
  font: 400 0.62rem/1 var(--sans);
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.rs-hero__audio {
  width: 100%;
  height: 36px;
  accent-color: var(--gold);
}
.rs-hero__social {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
}
.rs-social-link {
  width: 32px; height: 32px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
  transition: color 0.15s;
}
.rs-social-link:hover { color: var(--gold); opacity: 1; }
.rs-social-link svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; fill: currentColor; }

/* ══ PERCORSO ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.rs-percorso {
  background: var(--white);
  padding: 6rem var(--pad);
}
.rs-percorso__inner {
  max-width: 760px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.rs-section-head { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
.rs-section-title {
  font: 300 clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem)/1.15 var(--serif);
  color: var(--black);
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.rs-section-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
.rs-section-sub {
  font: 300 0.95rem/1.7 var(--sans);
  color: var(--muted);
}
.rs-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.rs-step {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 3rem 1fr;
  gap: 0 1.75rem;
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.rs-step__n {
  font: 300 2.2rem/0.9 var(--serif);
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0.6;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  padding-top: 0.2rem;
}
.rs-step__tag {
  display: block;
  font: 700 0.58rem/1 var(--sans);
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.rs-step__title {
  font: 700 1.15rem/1.25 var(--sans);
  color: var(--black);
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}
.rs-step__desc {
  font: 300 0.9rem/1.7 var(--sans);
  color: rgba(10,10,10,0.6);
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  max-width: 520px;
